Package: HerringData
Type: Package
Title: Load and wrangle Pacific Herring (*Clupea pallasii*) data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given = c("Matthew", "H"), family = "Grinnell",
    role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "matthew.grinnell@dfo-mpo.gc.ca")
Maintainer: Matthew Grinnell <matthew.grinnell@dfo-mpo.gc.ca>
Description: Load Pacific Herring (*Clupea pallasii*) data from databases and
    wrangle for data summary reports and input to statistical catch-age models.
    Data includes biological (number- and weight-at-age), catch, and spawn
    index data.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/grinnellm/HerringData
BugReports: https://github.com/grinnellm/HerringData/issues
Language: en-CA
ByteCompile: true
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Suggests: knitr, rmarkdown, tidyverse, here, magrittr, testthat, spelling,
    scales
Imports: DBI, Rdpack, dplyr, tibble, SpawnIndex, lubridate, odbc, tidyr, zoo,
    sf, tidyselect
Note: Requires access to DFO databases.
VignetteBuilder: knitr
RdMacros: Rdpack
Config/testthat/edition: 3
